<p>[[Companies]] affect people, communities, animals and the natural environment. Wikirate's Topics are an effort to organize these impact areas to allow for patterned [[Review]] assessing different [[Companies']] performance.</p>
<p>Each Topic page contains lists of [[Review]] about how specific [[Companies]] perform in that area.</p>
